            <h2 class="archive__item-title">Reconstructing the habitat of the first photosynthetic eukaryote</h2>
          

          
            <div class="archive__item-excerpt">
              <p>I used to obsessively watch the Simpsons and nature documentaries. On family vacations to Orlando, while my parents and sister lounged by the pool working on their tans, I ran around trying to catch brown anoles. They’d come home with the nicer tan, but I was eventually paid to catch anoles.</p>

