        <div class="archive__item-body">
          
            <h2 class="archive__item-title">I got my BSc at the University of Toronto in Human Biology and History</h2>
          

          
            <div class="archive__item-excerpt">
              <p>It took time to realize where my passions lay, but along the way I met wonderful people and learned about diverse subjects in history, music, philosophy, and biology. I was very fortunate to be apart of three different labs during my time at U of T. My responsibilities ranged from dishwasher to research student, but at every stage I was exposed to interesting ecological and evolutionary ideas.</p>

